This premium brush has rounded tipped bristles that make sure that even while detangling the toughest of knots your scalp doesn’t get irritated. The continuous motion of these tips also gives your scalp a stimulating massage. A sturdy handle with the name Vega written on it, gives you a good grip which is useful for smoothing out stubborn tangles or snags. After a good brushing, your hair shines and sleekly falls without any unsightly tangles. Ideal for medium to long hair lengths, this paddle brush makes sure that your hair is neat and tidy from root to tip. With Vega paddle brush you can flaunt straight and luxurious locks that is sure to attract admirers.
